Rithu Maria Jose

About

Rithu Maria Jose is pursuing Btech in Computer Science Engineering at College of Engineering Chengannur, Kerala, India. Presently she is serving as the Initiative Lead (Research Assistance) of IEEE Computer Society Student & Young Professional Activities R10 - India Committee, Chairperson of IEEE Women in Engineering Affinity Group College of Engineering Chengannur, and also a Quilt Committee Member of AnitaB. She's has volunteered for multiple forums/groups/non-profit organizations during her college and has organized 50+ events for students, especially for women, minorities and allies in tech to improve their technical as well as interpersonal skills.

She's a young talent exhibiting strength in innovative thinking and advance problem-solving, and having excellent interpersonal skills, communication abilities along with good verbal skills and a wide range of technical skills, she can become an asset to any organization.

In a short, she have been lucky enough to meet and work with a lot of amazing people, create some awesome content and inspire and make small changes in this prodigious world.
